### A13. HTTP Compression + Cache Headers (HIGH — addresses ISSUE-19, ISSUE-20)

**Problem**: Plan targets "< 300KB gzipped" but never enables gzip. A3 adds X-headers but no Cache-Control.

**1. Reverse Proxy Compression** (in nginx.conf — part of A4 Docker):
```nginx
# gzip for dynamic responses
gzip on;
gzip_types application/json text/plain text/css application/javascript;
gzip_min_length 1024;
gzip_comp_level 6;
gzip_vary on;

# brotli (if module available)
brotli on;
brotli_types application/json text/plain text/css application/javascript;
brotli_comp_level 6;
```

**2. Vite Build-Time Precompression** (in vite.config.ts):
```bash
cd frontend && npm install vite-plugin-compression -D
```
```typescript
import viteCompression from 'vite-plugin-compression';
// In plugins array:
viteCompression({ algorithm: 'gzip' }),
viteCompression({ algorithm: 'brotliCompress', ext: '.br' }),
```

**3. HTTP Cache Header Middleware**:
```php
// app/Http/Middleware/HttpCacheHeaders.php
class HttpCacheHeaders
{
    private const IMMUTABLE_PATTERNS = [
        'api/v5/support-service-groups',
        'api/v5/worklog-activity-types',
        'api/v5/support-sla-configs',
    ];

    public function handle(Request $request, Closure $next): Response
    {
        $response = $next($request);

        if (!$request->isMethod('GET') || !$response->isSuccessful()) {
            return $response;
        }

        // Static catalogs: cache 1 hour
        foreach (self::IMMUTABLE_PATTERNS as $pattern) {
            if ($request->is($pattern)) {
                $response->headers->set('Cache-Control', 'public, max-age=3600, s-maxage=3600');
                $response->headers->set('ETag', md5($response->getContent()));
                return $response;
            }
        }

        // User-specific data: private, short cache
        $response->headers->set('Cache-Control', 'private, no-cache, must-revalidate');
        $response->headers->set('Vary', 'Authorization, Cookie');

        return $response;
    }
}
```

**Static assets** (served by nginx):
```nginx
location /assets/ {
    expires 1y;
    add_header Cache-Control "public, max-age=31536000, immutable";
}
```

